data.description: Wonderful home in Enterprise that is ready for its new owners. This 3 bed/2 bath home has an open concept living floor plan and a fully equipped kitchen. The garage has been converted to a bonus room that could be used as a 4th bedroom. The oversized backyard has a concrete pad that is perfect for enjoying the upcoming fall nights. New roof being installed Nov 2023. Come take a look at this beautiful home before it's gone!
